==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Etymology===
From [[Serbo-Croatian]] [[šljivovica]] < Serbo-Croatian word for plum: [[šljiva]].
===Noun===
#A type of [[rakija]] made of distilled, fermented [[plum]] juice.  It is sometimes referred to as ''plum brandy''.
